515
00:27:32,255 --> 00:27:33,436
Not at all.

516
00:27:35,255 --> 00:27:37,916
Are you that afraid
to sleep on the same bed as me?

517
00:27:39,216 --> 00:27:41,156
I... I'm not afraid.

518
00:27:41,775 --> 00:27:44,516
Are you nervous, then?

519
00:27:45,696 --> 00:27:48,315
That's not it.

520
00:27:50,176 --> 00:27:52,436
I'm just

521
00:27:53,335 --> 00:27:55,156
not used to it yet.

522
00:27:57,255 --> 00:27:59,075
If so, you can take your time.

523
00:28:00,495 --> 00:28:03,676
Go to sleep now. Good night.

